 Li7-khui Vancouver goan2 koh che7 he2-chhia, keng-ke3 Lok8-ki soaN lai5 kau3 chit e5 sou2-chai7. Ka-na2-tai7 e5 he2-chhia put-chi2 toa7 tiuN. Mi5-si5 u7 pi7-pan7 bin5-chhng5, jit8-si5 u7 chau3-kha thang hou7 lang5 chu2-chiah8. An2-ni sou2-hui3 khah seng2. Na7-si7 ti7 chhia-lai7 sit8-tong5 chiah8, tak8 hang7 chin kui3. Koe-nng7 1 liap8 4 kak gun5, keng-chio chit8 koeh 6 kak gun5, kam-a2 chit8 liap8 7 kak. Na7-si7 ti7 chhia-lai7 u7 thih-chau3, ka-ki7 pi7-pan7 chiu7 chin seng2. Ti7 chhia-lai7 goan2 tak8 tng3 u7 chu2-png7, put-chi2 li7-pian7 kap sim-sek. Pat8 e5 tah-kheh put-chi2 piaN3-se3, long2 si7 ko-teng2 e5 chong2-phou3, chin gau5 chu2. Keng-ke3 Lok8-ki soaN, keng2-ti3 kau3-kek8 sui2. SoaN-teng2 long2 si7 seh, soaN-kha si7 chhiu7-na5 kap chhan5-hng5. Na7-si7 koan5 e5 soaN long2 si7 chit8 ban7 chhioh i2-siong7. Lok8-ki soaN ke3 liau2 (2 jit8, 1 mi5) chiu7 keng-ke3 chit8 e5 toa7 piN5-iuN5. Chit e5 sou2-chai7 chhut beh8 kap gu5, be2 chin choe7. 
 Hian7-chai7 goan2 tiam3 chit e5 sou2-chai7 si7 ti7 chng-nih8, khah koan5 hai2 1800 chhioh. ThiN-khi3 ti7 chia put-chi2 leng2; cha7-hng kap kin-a2-jit8 u7 loh8 seh; chui2 ti7 goa7-bin7 u7 kian peng poaN3-chhun3 kau7. Na7-si7 lin2 ti7 Tai5-oan5 teh iat8-siN3 chin joah8. Ti7 chit chng-nih8 sou2-chai7 e5 peh-siN3 put-chi2 khai-hoa3 kap bun5-beng5. Choh-sit lang5 khah choe7 ka-ki7 u7 chu7-tong7-chhia. Chhu3-lai7 ke-ke hou7-hou7 ia7 u7 tian7-oe7. Teng2 le2-pai3 goan2 ti7 chit8 keng chng-nih8 e5 kong-hak8-hau7 choe3 le2-pai3. Chu2-li2 le2-pai3--e5, si7 chit8 e5 choh-sit lang5; jih8-khim5--e5, si7 tai7-hak8 e5 chut-giap8-seng. U7 6 tiuN chu7-tong7-chhia kap 2 tiuN be2-chhia chai3 chiah-e5 choh-sit lang5 khi3 le2-pai3. Chhia long2 si7 in ka-ki7 e5. 
 Hian7-chai7 goan2 toa3 e5 sou2-chai7 li7 chit e5 sio2 koe-chhi7 phou3 poaN3 lou7. Chit e5 koe-chhi7 chi2-u7 700 lang5. Iau2-ku2 sou2-chai7 put-chi2 hoat-tat8. U7 3 e5 i-seng, 3 e5 pian7-hou7-su7, 4 keng le2-pai3-tng5, chit8 keng lu2-koan2 3 chan3 lau5, chit8 keng sio2-hak8-hau7, chit8 keng tiong-hak8-hau7, ia7 chit8 kham2 tiam3 kap Hu2-cheng5-koe siong7 toa7 kham2-e5 piN5 toa7. 
 Cha7-hng koe-nih8 e5 lang5 u7 chhiaN2 goan2 khi3 ian2-soat. Goa2 u7 kong2-khi2 Tam7-chui2 Tiong Hak8-hau7 e5 su7 hou7 in thiaN. In put-chi2 ai3 chai lan2 Tai5-oan5 e5 tai7-chi3. 
 Koh nng7 le2-pai3 goan2 beh li7-khui chia khi3 To-lun5-to siaN5. To-lun5-to si7 toa7 sou2-chai7 u7 50 goa7 ban7 lang5. Tui3 chia kau3 hia, che7 he2-chhia tioh8 3 jit8 ku2. Ng3-bang7 ti7-hia tit-tioh8 ho2 ki-hoe7 thang po3 in chai lan2 Tai5-oan5 e5 siau-sit. 
 Chit tiuN phoe kau3 ui7 e5 si5 lin2 i2-keng teh chhi3-giam7. Bang7 lin2 tai7-ke sio2-sim chiau3-kou3 lin2 e5 sin-the2. Ia7 siong5-siong5 ti3-i3 po2-siu2 lin2 e5 phin2-heng7. Goan7 lan2 e5 ThiN-pe7 jit8-jit8 chiau3-kou3 pi3-iu7 lin2. 
